            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/3bf22c7b1f99db8781e5e2aa8ac53b1b20e9cb62695bd1bb8dac4224b22292e1.jpg"
                },
                "image_caption": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(b）"
                    }
                ],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                268,
                243,
                747,
                342
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "list",
            "content": {
                "list_type": "text_list",
                "list_items": [
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "在（a）与（b）中，R和B分别取领域的平均值。"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "在（c）与（d）中，取领域的 4 个 B 或 R 的均值作为中间像素的 B 值。"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                236,
                387,
                786,
                425
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "2) 插值绿算法实现 "
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                206,
                426,
                366,
                442
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/2a80487c8eea4fc869e7635c929cae3802d26bf5c631ad1d1d7904f69c8b5d33.jpg"
                },
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                248,
                451,
                546,
                606
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/c28cfac900f5965db27b723163eaaee8a3b56068f8977fb110f2cd7502aa114e.jpg"
                },
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                628,
                451,
                929,
                608
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "由于人眼对绿光反应最敏感，对紫光和红光则反应较弱，因此为了达到更好的画质，需要对G特殊照顾。在上述（c）与（d）中，扩展开来就是上图的（e）与（f）中间像素G的取值，这也有一定的算法要求，不同的算法效果上会有差异。经过相关的研究，（e）中间像素G值的算法如下："
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                236,
                667,
                843,
                739
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "equation_interline",
            "content": {
                "math_content": "G (R) = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l l} \\frac {G 1 + G 3}{2} & , | R 1 - R 3 | <   | R 2 - R 4 | \\\\ \\frac {G 3 + G 4}{2} & , | R 1 - R 3 | > | R 2 - R 4 | \\\\ \\frac {G 1 + G 2 + G 3 + G 4}{4} & , | R 1 - R 3 | = | R 2 - R 4 | \\end{array} \\right.",
                "math_type": "latex",
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/dd5a03bbbccab696cf2d11991ab542141d091f4617c710a19557f4cb92fd677b.jpg"
                }
            },
            "bbox": [
                290,
                753,
                742,
                875
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "（f）中间像素G值的算法如下："
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                247,
                889,
                489,
                906
            ]
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "equation_interline",
            "content": {
                "math_content": "G (B) = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l l} \\frac {G 1 + G 3}{2} & , | B 1 - B 3 | <   | B 2 - B 4 | \\\\ \\frac {G 3 + G 4}{2} & , | B 1 - B 3 | > | B 2 - B 4 | \\\\ \\frac {G 1 + G 2 + G 3 + G 4}{4} & , | B 1 - B 3 | = | B 2 - B 4 | \\end{array} \\right.",
                "math_type": "latex",
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/896c567875471e86204ae658b398603b160dbed15ef352589bcd781aca22b2f4.jpg"
                }
            },
            "bbox": [
                255,
                112,
                692,
                236
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "CMOS摄像头这部分转换是在内部用ADC或者ISP完成的，生产商为了降低成本必然会使得图像失真。当然用外部处理器来实现转换，如果处理器的速度足够NB，能够胜任像素的操作，用上面的算法来进行转换，皆大欢喜。不过上述算法将直接成倍提高了算法的复杂度，速度上将会有所限制。因此为了速度的提成，可以直接通过来4领域G取均值来中间像素的G值，将会降低一倍的速率，而在性能上差之甚微，算法如下："
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                236,
                260,
                848,
                369
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "equation_interline",
            "content": {
                "math_content": "G (R) = \\frac {G 1 + G 2 + G 3 + G 4}{4} \\text {或} G (B) = \\frac {G 1 + G 2 + G 3 + G 4}{4}",
                "math_type": "latex",
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/3146901b27801ec73df9c4325c2946858741cc27bf3d7ab518373e8dba4ed328.jpg"
                }
            },
            "bbox": [
                257,
                387,
                729,
                428
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "如果能够通过损失图像的质量，来达到更快的速度，还可以取G1、G2的均值来实现，但是这样的做法会导致边沿以及跳变部分的失真。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                236,
                445,
                843,
                481
            ]
        }
    ]
]